    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, it breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-stored, and followed every service to a T. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for an adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
