    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E36 M3, featuring its original S50B30 inline-six with a fully serviced VANOS unit and verified factory-spec compression. This specimen utilizes a precise ZF 5-speed manual transmission paired with a 3.15 limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains structurally pristine, benefiting from reinforced subframe mounting points and a refreshed suspension geometry featuring OEM-spec Bilstein dampers and polyurethane bushings. The exterior maintains a concours-level finish, while the interior 'Vader' seats show no bolster wear, preserving the tactile integrity of the original Nappa leather. This is an analog masterpiece with a documented service history, free of any parasitic draws or mechanical lash.",
      "price": 46500.0,
