    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom condition, looking and driving exactly as it did the day it was first delivered. The exterior paintwork is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like luster with no chips, swirls, or imperfections, having been kept exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the hand-stitched leather is supple and unmarked, the high-gloss trim is free of scratches, and every feature\u2014from the premium sound system to the advanced climate control\u2014operates with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a meticulous service record performed exclusively by master technicians using genuine parts. The engine bay is detailed to a high standard, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This is a rare opportunity to own a top-tier example of this model that satisfies even the most rigorous inspection. Truly a collector-grade find for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
